{"id": "1496197454788563004", "channel_id": "1496197454788563004", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131442594275151883", "author_name": "leo6423", "author_bot": false, "content": "我也算之前测试版牢玩家了，测试结束后就没再关注。后来在b站刷到沙耶之歌联动视频才知道原来国际服早就开服了<:please:1356053110375714817> 。大概一个半月前入坑的，一周前刚打完第七章，现在融灾能比较轻松打个330。自己配的5个融灾队（希洛那个队借莫夏助战）但是感觉其中两个（图鲁和小水母）都比较弱，于是抽了个阿拉科涅看看能不能另外组个队踢掉水母队。看魔龙大佬说是最好配反击或者毒角，但是他推荐的宁非亚看榜单里有点太弱了（而且有点不合xp），想问下潘迪亚，凯科斯，以及另外一个毒蜘蛛能不能当c和阿拉科涅配队。以及能不能帮我看看我配的几个队怎么改和问下后续抽卡建议（有点想抽淡忘墨菲）。感谢大家<:Helot_slack_off:1459092159465521184>", "timestamp": "2026-04-21T17:14:31.226000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1496197456998699169", "filename": "1.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 5194381, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496197454788563004/1496197456998699169/1.PNG?ex=69e901f7&is=69e7b077&hm=6f0f8dab50273970cf4d3bffda9356b369688eccac7da4e54dfd9516df634881&"}, {"id": "1496197458286612631", "filename": "2.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 5019038, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496197454788563004/1496197458286612631/2.PNG?ex=69e901f8&is=69e7b078&hm=ae4d58aa927da551811367c745e7671e123bf3400d953003ecb4a69d0258d6c5&"}, {"id": "1496197459217486076", "filename": "3.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 5031463, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496197454788563004/1496197459217486076/3.PNG?ex=69e901f8&is=69e7b078&hm=60c3d4ad092614b1f7900cf8d322bb1bccd17302ca77a5f79c13607a3e92eef8&"}, {"id": "1496197460090159225", "filename": "4.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4903230, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496197454788563004/1496197460090159225/4.PNG?ex=69e901f8&is=69e7b078&hm=b4c260145952d4740aa009946d95c6e05d9c7ad2e9c819d98016fae4e93e0230&"}, {"id": "1496197460861784167", "filename": "5.PNG", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4514976, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496197454788563004/1496197460861784167/5.PNG?ex=6